⭐ Manager's Favorite Questions

Authentication vs Authorization

Authentication → Who are you?

Authorization → What can you do?


---

OAuth vs OIDC

OAuth → Authorization

OIDC → Authentication + Authorization


---

ID Token vs Access Token

ID Token → Client → Identity

Access Token → API → Authorization


---

SSO vs SAML

SSO → Business concept

SAML → Protocol implementing SSO


---

IdP vs SP

IdP → Authenticates users (Entra)

SP → Provides service (Claude)


